---
title: Pesto & Cherry Tomato Israeli Couscous Salad with Feta & Almonds Quick Prep | Ready in 15 | Serves 2
description: Got fifteen quick minutes to give this lunch idea a go? Introducing a wholesome dish featuring Israeli couscous with silky baby spinach and basil pesto melted into it, plus a burst of sweetness from the cherry tomatoes. The only thing that could make this better is some crumbly feta to go over the top. Oh wait, we've got that too! Enjoy.
